{"tid":1877283,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【陀衰家】中國廠商堅持參展，MWC2020直接取消","createTime":"2020-02-13T02:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T03:28:10.000Z","uid":52763,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1ac3ad7979c11c526738c87e9be46bb1dc95c7bf","tid":1877283,"uid":52763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:30:44.000Z","msg":"考量到武漢肺炎疫情，多家大廠已宣布不會參加今年的世界通訊大會，據傳主辦方GSMA也<br />\n在開會商討，是否要停辦巴賽隆納MWC 202<br />\n<br />\n英特爾、臉書、NTT、AT&amp;T也退展，MWC 2020官方周五決議是否停辦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎（COVID-19）陰影下，巴賽隆納MWC 2020退展名單愈來愈長。在LG、愛立信、<br />\nNvidia、Sony、Amazon後，又有晶片大廠英特爾、臉書、AT&amp;T及NTT Docomo、思科等，宣<br />\n布不參加今年的世界通訊大會（World Mobile Congress，MWC）。<br />\n<br />\n原本今年MWC上電信業者可望會有大量5G的消息宣布，但在疫情影響下，美國電信業者<br />\nAT&amp;T及日本電信公司NTT Docomo，雙雙宣布退出。AT&amp;T Business事業部執行長Anne Chow<br />\n原本預定，在MWC發表致詞演講。AT&amp;T表示，在經過討論與計畫後，AT&amp;T決定不參加今年<br />\nMWC。AT&amp;T尊敬主辦方GSMA保護參加者的一切措施，但他們認為最負責的決定，是退出展<br />\n覽以維護員工和客戶的健康。<br />\n<br />\nNTT Docomo也表示考量員工和客戶健康，該公司決定不參加MWC 2020，是繼Sony後，第二<br />\n家退出的日本公司。至於社長吉澤和弘原本預定到場發表演說的行程，NTT Docomo 表示<br />\n還在討論是否取消。<br />\n<br />\n晶片大廠英特爾發布聲明稿表示，員工與夥伴的健康與福祉是公司第一要務，謹慎起見，<br />\n英特爾已退出今年MWC，他們感謝主辦單位的諒解，並表示期待參加未來的MWC。另一家晶<br />\n片業者聯發科，也決定不前往巴賽隆納。<br />\n<br />\n社群龍頭臉書表示，武漢肺炎（COVID-19）相關公衛風險升高，臉書決定員工不會參加今<br />\n年的MWC。<br />\n<br />\n其他不參展名單包括網通設備業者思科、中國手機業者Vivo。而中國家電業者TCL和中興<br />\n（ZTE）一樣，只取消記者會但仍會參展。<br />\n<br />\n退展大廠已經太多，而且可能還會持續增加。退展相關損失其實是由參展廠商負擔，GSMA<br />\n本身並沒有太大損失。但是GSMA擔心的是，大廠不參加將使大會失色。AndroidPolice報<br />\n導，原本表示仍會舉行MWC 2020的GSMA，將在本周開會商討是否停辦今年巴賽隆納MWC<br />\n2020的活動。"},{"pid":"74549f1dcf4f3e3f8e66d1a6ab058a42bd649dea","tid":1877283,"uid":177089,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:36:59.000Z","msg":"笑死 躝返支那啦支那人"},{"pid":"bf5018489fa1bd037e8f1ee800029b3e14895579","tid":1877283,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc12de50b1606ff4af35d7f86f77beaafed23b7a","tid":1877283,"uid":55384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0973a4423ecfed3e8c9c694b759d13ae2f1f936e","tid":1877283,"uid":33868,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:41:02.000Z","msg":"華為自己去武漢搞番場"},{"pid":"3d2d6cffe2bf15fd0961bcbb0c21d574bdd82940","tid":1877283,"uid":327447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:41:38.000Z","msg":"MWC2020已宣佈取消"},{"pid":"b88194d6694c9436d9d02a915a5a7f72df40fca0","tid":1877283,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞番個 no China 版"},{"pid":"ed546b1629ef09f673352ae4d942f0c9fc6f8a0d","tid":1877283,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"支那當然死都想繼續，因為今年重點講5G"},{"pid":"8b27f3afcb93cc7ca091ea35b65dba2f0bcc79f8","tid":1877283,"uid":66049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:45:18.000Z","msg":"可以考慮喺湖北搞<br />\n支那自己圍爐"},{"pid":"877aee7cce455f6a9cffc7ea3d2871eaaf0aa6e8","tid":1877283,"uid":277702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:45:39.000Z","msg":"忽然之間財神變瘟神<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e630e06acfceb6868dcd706b60554d75c2c807","tid":1877283,"uid":67771,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8b27f3afcb93cc7ca091ea35b65dba2f0bcc79f8","tid":1877283,"uid":66049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:45:18.000Z","msg":"可以考慮喺湖北搞<br />\n支那自己圍爐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:47:48.000Z","msg":"Mobile Wuhan Congress, 中囯又贏"},{"pid":"f97ace8c73cdb219f79033e56f59dd227a16bea7","tid":1877283,"uid":197563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:03:58.000Z","msg":"呢件事2001年已經應該要發生"},{"pid":"2f0060a86f1bdbd153dd223f0eeabecc650f181d","tid":1877283,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T03:28:10.000Z","msg":"四面樹敵 八面威風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}